            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je disais au fils d'épicure :\n\" réveillez par vos joyeux chants\nParny, qui sait de la nature\nCélébrer les plus doux penchants. \"\nMais les chants que la joie inspire\nFont place aux regrets superflus :\nIl vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Je disais aux graces émues :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "\" il vous doit sa célébrité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Montrez-vous à lui demi-nues ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il peigne encor la volupté. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Mais chacune d'elles soupire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Auprès des plaisirs éperdus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Il vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je disais aux graces émues :\n\" il vous doit sa célébrité.\nMontrez-vous à lui demi-nues ;\nQu'il peigne encor la volupté. \"\nMais chacune d'elles soupire\nAuprès des plaisirs éperdus.\nIl vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Je disais aux dieux du bel âge :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "\" amours, rendez à ses vieux ans",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Les fleurs qu'aux pieds d'une volage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Il prodigua dans son printemps. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Mais en pleurant je les vois lire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Des vers qu'ils ont cent fois relus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Il vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je disais aux dieux du bel âge :\n\" amours, rendez à ses vieux ans\nLes fleurs qu'aux pieds d'une volage\nIl prodigua dans son printemps. \"\nMais en pleurant je les vois lire\nDes vers qu'ils ont cent fois relus.\nIl vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Je disais aux muses plaintives :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "\" oubliez vos malheurs récents ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Pour charmer l'écho de nos rives,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Il vous suffit de ses accents. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Mais du poétique délire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Elles brisent les attributs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Il vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je disais aux muses plaintives :\n\" oubliez vos malheurs récents ;\nPour charmer l'écho de nos rives,\nIl vous suffit de ses accents. \"\nMais du poétique délire\nElles brisent les attributs.\nIl vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Il n'est plus ! Ah ! Puisse l'envie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "S'interdire un dernier effort !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Immortel il quitte la vie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Pour lui tous les dieux sont d'accord.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Que la haine, prête à maudire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Pardonne aux aimables vertus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Il vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il n'est plus ! Ah ! Puisse l'envie\nS'interdire un dernier effort !\nImmortel il quitte la vie ;\nPour lui tous les dieux sont d'accord.\nQue la haine, prête à maudire,\nPardonne aux aimables vertus.\nIl vient d'expirer sur sa lyre :"
        }
    ],
